/-- Claim `S2-agent-interior-relative-ball-closure-source`.

The exact `interior_relative_ball_closure` row is reduced to the honest local
exterior-side witness: nearby points on the same open canonical segment are
limits of points in the unbounded exterior component.  The conversion itself
is just the metric closure criterion, leaving the residual geometric/topology
work as `InteriorEdgeNearbyExteriorPointSource`. -/
theorem S2_agent_interior_relative_ball_closure_source
    {C : _root_.UDConfig n}
    {inputs : FinitePlanarOuterComponentInputs C}
    (nearby_edge_point_exterior_points :
      InteriorEdgeNearbyExteriorPointSource C inputs) :
    InteriorRelativeBallClosureRow C inputs := by
  intro e p he hpEdge hpFrontier
  exact
    relative_ball_closure_of_forall_nearby_edge_point_exterior_points
