Raw face-successor boundary-edge adapter for an already identified concrete
cycle boundary.  The boundary edge row is transported from the actual
consecutive raw-orbit edge membership, not recovered from a downstream
spanning-cycle projection. -/
theorem S2_agent_raw_orbit_boundary_edge_mem_source
    {C : _root_.UDConfig n}
    {inputs : FinitePlanarOuterComponentInputs C}
    {R : UnitDistanceRotationSystem C}
    {start : UnitDistanceDart C}
    (B : JordanBoundaryConcrete.UnitDistanceCycleBoundary C)
